Subject: EasyForm — here's what to send
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"></head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:24px 12px;background:#f1f5f9;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;color:#0f172a">
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;width:100%;background:#fff;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 24px -8px rgba(15,23,42,0.15)">
  <tr><td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4f46e5,#9333ea);padding:24px 28px;color:#fff">
    <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:22px;font-weight:700">Welcome to EasyForm 👋</h1>
    <p style="margin:6px 0 0;font-size:14px;opacity:0.92">Here's everything we need to fill your government exam application</p>
  </td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:24px 28px">
    <p>Hi <strong>{{ candidate_name or "there" }}</strong>,</p>
    <p>Thanks for getting in touch! Just reply to this email with the documents and details below and we'll auto-fill your exam form for you.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#4f46e5;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:24px 0 8px;border-bottom:2px solid #4f46e5;padding-bottom:6px">📎 Documents to attach</h2>
    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse">
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;width:46%;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">10th Class Marksheet</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">PDF or JPG/PNG</td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">12th Class Marksheet</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">with the stream visible</td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">Graduation Marksheet</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">final consolidated</td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">Post-Graduation Marksheet</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">if applicable</td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">Passport-size Photo</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">clear face, plain background</td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">Signature</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">scan/photo on white</td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:14px">Aadhaar or PAN Card</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px">for ID + permanent address</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2 style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#4f46e5;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:24px 0 8px;border-bottom:2px solid #4f46e5;padding-bottom:6px">✍️ In the email body</h2>
    <p style="margin:0 0 10px;font-size:14px">Mention these details that aren't on your documents (or are likely outdated):</p>
    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse">
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;width:46%;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">Marital Status</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">Single / Married / …</td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">Nationality</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">usually Indian</td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">Category / Caste</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">General / OBC / SC / ST / EWS</td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">Mobile Number</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">your active 10-digit number</td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">Correspondence Address</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0">where you currently reside + PIN code</td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:8px 10px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:14px">Disability Status</td><td style="padding:8px 10px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px">"None", or describe</td></tr>
    </table>

    <div style="margin:24px 0 0;padding:16px 18px;background:#eef2ff;border:1px solid #c7d2fe;border-radius:10px">
      <strong style="color:#3730a3;font-size:13.5px">You can write naturally — no rigid format needed.</strong>
      <p style="margin:8px 0 0;font-size:13.5px;color:#334155">Example: <em>"I am single, Indian, OBC. My mobile is 9876543210. My correspondence address is Flat 12, Sector 5, Noida — 201301. I have no disability."</em></p>
      <p style="margin:8px 0 0;font-size:13.5px;color:#334155">Then attach your marksheets, photo, signature, and Aadhaar (or PAN).</p>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top:24px;font-size:13.5px;color:#334155">Once you've sent everything, we'll process your documents and email you a review with all the extracted details for you to confirm before submission. If anything is missing or unclear we'll ask specifically what we need.</p>

    <p style="margin-top:18px;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8">Keep the subject line containing the word "EasyForm" so we route your emails correctly. Reference ID: {{ user_id }}</p>
    <p style="margin:4px 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8">— EasyForm</p>
  </td></tr>
</table>
</body></html>
